&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;The Associate Engineer is a mid-level position in the engineering department, responsible for professional engineering work related to the planning, design, construction, and maintenance of various public works projects. Under direction and minimal supervision, an Associate Engineer performs design of public works projects, coordinates with other project staff, activities and tasks, provides technical support for internal and external stakeholders, and acts as a supervisor to a small group of assistant engineers and/or technical staff.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;fr-view&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Perform engineering calculations, and prepare plans, specifications and estimates for construction of public works projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Under direction and minimal supervision, perform complex engineering work for public works projects, ensuring technical competence and compliance with governing regulations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Coordinate project activities with all stakeholders including but not limited to the project team, field personnel, agency staff, utility companies, other consultants, and contractors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Maintain knowledge of the latest Caltrans and/or AASHTO design and construction standards and specifications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Work closely with clients and project teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
